<subSubSection pageId="284" pageNumber="285" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="284.[151,1437,1412,1653]" pageId="284" pageNumber="285">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,511,1556,1581]" pageId="284" pageNumber="285">Distribution and habitat.</emphasis>
<collectingRegion box="[525,677,1556,1581]" country="Papua New Guinea" name="New Ireland" pageId="284" pageNumber="285">New Ireland</collectingRegion>
: 1, 2.—General distribution: Red Sea, East Africa, 
<collectingCountry box="[1309,1432,1556,1581]" name="Seychelles" pageId="284" pageNumber="285">Seychelles</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[151,286,1591,1616]" name="Madagascar" pageId="284" pageNumber="285">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
and Mascarenes east to Rotuma and 
<collectingCountry box="[727,799,1593,1617]" name="Tonga" pageId="284" pageNumber="285">Tonga</collectingCountry>
, north to southern 
<collectingCountry box="[1023,1090,1593,1616]" name="Japan" pageId="284" pageNumber="285">Japan</collectingCountry>
, south to 
<collectingCountry box="[1208,1386,1591,1616]" name="New Caledonia" pageId="284" pageNumber="285">New Caledonia</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[151,257,1628,1653]" name="Australia" pageId="284" pageNumber="285">Australia</collectingCountry>
